{
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "description": "Project Alexandria — MCP Knowledge Base. Monitored via Sauron (Helldiver Squadron Beta). Hub-side Blackbox HTTP probing of GitHub Pages docs site only — the MCP server itself runs via stdio and has no HTTP interface.",
